page.title: 07JOBS IN CATTERLINE
page.content: There are quite a lot of people with jobs in Catterline. There are three fishermen. Catterline was famous for its artists. Around Catterline there are lots of farmers. There is one builder who lives in Catterline. There is one electrician and there is one publican who owns a pub. In Catterline there are lots of people who are retired. There is a school in the village. Cooks work here and there is a cleaner who comes to clean the school. There is also a part-time lady janitor. There is a doctor and a dentist who live in our area as well. There are two teachers in our school. They don't live here,they just work here. There is also a detective who lives in Catterline. Some people live in Catterline but don't work here.
